OL,3,CHeinz and Mattel join forces to create
OL,4,Cpink 'Barbiecue' sauce
OL,6,FHeinz and Mattel have unleashed their
OL,7,Fcollaboration in homage to Barbie.
OL,9,FThe brands joined forces to launch a
OL,10,Fpink vegan mayo named 'Barbiecue'
OL,11,Fsauce.
OL,13,FIt follows last year's 'Barbiecore'
OL,14,Fcraze around the blockbuster movie,
OL,15,Fand arrives in time to coincide with
OL,16,Fthe 65th anniversary of the Barbie
OL,17,Fbrand.
