OL,6,FThe studio behind the box office hit
OL,7,Ffilm previously announced it had
OL,8,Fcontributed more than #80 million to
OL,9,Fthe UK economy and created 685 jobs.
OL,11,FThe film was largely shot at Leavesden
OL,12,Fstudios in Hertfordshire, where Gerwig
OL,13,Fcreated the detailed and vivid
OL,14,FBarbieland sets.
OL,16,FIt generated more than #95 million at
OL,17,Fthe UK box office, the evidence says.
