OL,3,CHeinz and Mattel join forces to create
OL,4,Cpink 'Barbiecue' sauce
OL,6,FAn initial limited run of just 5,000
OL,7,F'Barbiecue' bottles will be available
OL,8,Ffrom Monday solely online, followed by
OL,9,Fanother limited run at retailers
OL,10,Fshortly afterwards.
OL,12,FHeinz said the smoky sauce included
OL,13,Fbeetroot extract to achieve the pink
OL,14,Fcolour.
OL,16,FThiago Rapp from Heinz, said: "Barbie
OL,17,Fwell and truly won the hearts of Brits
OL,18,Fall over again last year, and after
OL,19,Fseeing the reaction this sauce brought
OL,20,Fto our fans on social media, we knew
OL,21,Fwe had to make it a reality.
