OL,3,CHeinz and Mattel join forces to create
OL,4,Cpink 'Barbiecue' sauce
OL,6,F"We're always looking for ways to
OL,7,Finnovate and give our fans what they
OL,8,Fwant, and we're thrilled to be able to
OL,9,Fbring this iconic partnership with
OL,10,FMattel to life."
OL,12,FThe idea for the product began last
OL,13,Fsummer, with both brands explaining
OL,14,Fthey 'worked quickly' to bring the
OL,15,Fprospect of the product to life.
OL,17,FInitially developed in digital form,
OL,18,Fthe physical product will soon be
OL,19,Favailable.
